Simulate Data

Source: R/manMetaVAR-gen-data.R
GenData.Rd

The function simulates data using the simStateSpace::SimSSMIVary() function.

Usage

GenData(n, time)

Arguments

n

Positive integer. Sample size.

time

Positive integer. Number of time points.

Examples

if (FALSE) { # \dontrun{
set.seed(42)
data <- GenData(n = 50, time = 100)
plot(data)
} # }
